text: Hey @FedExHelp you delayed my package that is in the truck to be delivered today. Tomorrow is not acceptable. The agreement was today. Time to fix it.

@SteveOKruz Hi Steve, this is Kelly. I do apologize for any frustration or inconvenience. I will be happy to research. Please DM @FedExHelp with your address, city, state, zip code, tracking number, phone number and email address.
@SteveOKruz I have received your message. Please allow me time to look into the issue and send you a follow-up.
